@Node INTRODUCTION

Welcome to this first release of Shapeshifter's gamelist!
You have an Amiga...
You have Shapeshifter...
You want to by a Macintosh-compatible game but...does it work with Shapeshifter?
So I made it for you!
This guide was created especialy for Shapeshifter users. All the tests were based on demoversions found
into CD-ROM Magazines like SVM Mac or Univers MAC so I can't guarant you the 100% compatibility of the
full game...but there's no reason it doesn't work too!

